葉恭平博士專題演講會
Dr. G.P. Yeh Speech 
12月10日聖蓋博市希爾頓酒店免費公開演講
December 10, 2016, San Gabriel Hilton, CA 
1) 2:00 PM - 2:50 PM (including Q & A)
 
High Energy Physics, the Top Quark, and Advanced Technologies
高能物理、頂誇克和新高科技
10 minutes break 
2) 3:00 PM - 3:45 PM (including Q & A)
 
Particle Therapy
